1
00:00:12,120 --> 00:00:14,250
I can't believe a water dungeon exists

2
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:16,239
in the Young Master's manor.

3
00:00:20,680 --> 00:00:22,240
Such torturous methods,

4
00:00:22,520 --> 00:00:24,780
only Chu Shengyi could come up with them.

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,760
These injuries are too severe.

6
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:31,080
How long will it take to heal?

7
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:35,440
I used to think he married Qingcheng for money.

8
00:00:36,400 --> 00:00:37,880
But in that private prison,

9
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:38,880
to save my life,

10
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:40,810
I tested him with Yanzhi Pavilion.

11
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:43,600
Yet he wanted to kill me.

12
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:52,050
Chu Shengyi's purpose for getting Qingcheng

13
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:54,500
is definitely not simple.

14
00:00:54,720 --> 00:00:55,360
My lady,

15
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:57,400
maybe we should just leave.

16
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:59,100
This Young Master's manor

17
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:03,600
is a dragon's den.

18
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:06,320
The Third Young Master is treacherous and unpredictable.

19
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:08,240
I'm just afraid that if you deal with him for too long,

20
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:09,640
you might lose your life.

21
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:14,480
The Governor's Mansion is heavily guarded.

22
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,539
Without a summons,

23
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:17,620
we can't enter Qiwu Courtyard at all.

24
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:19,490
This is our only chance.

25
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:23,500
Where is the thing I asked for?

26
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,690
You were right, my lady.

27
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,780
It really was in the black market.

28
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,640
After the former Governor left,

29
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,400
the mansion was burglarized once.

30
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,520
The thieves in our Kuizhou are not stupid.

31
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:40,840
This map of the Governor's Mansion

32
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:43,570
is worth much more than ordinary gold and silver.

33
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,680
It's enough.

34
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:49,440
Qiwu Courtyard is in the southwest corner of the mansion.

35
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,880
And Madam Li

36
00:01:51,240 --> 00:01:53,900
usually holds banquets in the East Flower Hall.

37
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:56,600
We need to grow the flowers quickly.

38
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:15,520
So this is the new lowly girl taken in by the Third Young Master.

39
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,380
I heard she's also a flower slave.

40
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:20,880
The Grand Governor's Mansion has really made a joke of itself this time.

41
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:23,720
How does a mere flower slave deserve to sit with us?

42
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:27,880
Watch me make this flower slave embarrass herself at the banquet.

43
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:30,810
The Third Young Master is here. Keep your voice down.

44
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:40,760
What's wrong?

45
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:44,440
The cushion has been soaked in rice water.

46
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:46,120
Someone, go get a new one.

47
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,480
Why are you helping me?

48
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:55,280
You haven't told me the truth yet.

49
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,920
Naturally, I won't let anything happen to you.

50
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:58,640
Madam Li has arrived!

51
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:12,640
Mother.

52
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:22,010
Be careful, Mother.

53
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:31,040
Why is Lady Fang still standing?

54
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:35,079
Mother, my cushion is wet,

55
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,800
and a new one hasn't been brought yet.

56
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:39,800
We can't let the new bride stand like this all the time.

57
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:45,079
I'm fine, I can just sit like this.

58
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:50,200
This is not a street gathering.

59
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:52,770
Lady Fang comes from a humble background.

60
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:56,060
It's understandable she doesn't know the etiquette here.

61
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,260
But since she has entered your manor,

62
00:03:58,320 --> 00:04:00,280
she represents your face in the future.

63
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,540
You need to keep an eye on her at all times.

64
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,320
You are right, Mother.

65
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:05,050
Look at the Third Young Master.

66
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,140
Let the banquet begin.

67
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,560
Lady Fang has specially presented the hand-planted

68
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,760
Peony Zhaoyebai

69
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,560
to celebrate Madam Li's birthday.

70
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:16,200
Please extinguish the candles, ladies.

71
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,680
So beautiful! What a gorgeous flower!

72
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:24,200
I didn't expect this lowly girl to know how to grow flowers.

73
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,120
Mother,

74
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:28,080
this flower is called Zhaoyebai.

75
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:31,000
It glows brightly when the moonlight shines on it.

76
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,640
Today, I present this flower to celebrate your birthday,

77
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:36,600
wishing your blessings shine eternally like the moonlight,

78
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:39,320
bathing the entire Governor's Mansion in your clear light,

79
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,880
bringing brilliance to the courtyard,

80
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,480
and natural splendor.

81
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:46,120
They grew so well. So beautiful.

82
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,380
I've never seen anything like it.

83
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,200
So beautiful.

84
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,620
Absolutely gorgeous.

85
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,440
Guards,

86
00:04:58,840 --> 00:04:59,770
light the lamps.

87
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:09,440
What's wrong, Lady Fang?

88
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:15,080
Mother, my cold hadn't completely healed before I came.

89
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,290
Now that I've had a few cups of wine,

90
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:19,280
I feel dizzy

91
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:20,880
and my vision is blurring.

92
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,720
I'm afraid I might make a fool of myself here.

93
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:25,640
I'd like to rest in the side hall for a moment.

94
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:31,600
Momo, go check if Lady Fang is alright.

95
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,320
Yes.

96
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,880
Madam, Lady Fang does have a slight fever.

97
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:47,760
Then you may be excused.

98
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,120
Thank you, Mother.

99
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:54,520
Nanny,

100
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:57,740
prepare a maid's outfit and wait for me in the side hall.

101
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:00,240
The venom of a certain cactus thorn

102
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,840
can cause a temporary fever.

103
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,640
I'll slip away from the birthday banquet then

104
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:05,440
and look for you in the side hall.

105
00:06:16,280 --> 00:06:18,000
Based on Qiwu Courtyard's location on the map,

106
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,730
it should be in this direction.

107
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:10,560
Young Master.

108
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,920
Lady Fang indeed entered Qiwu Courtyard,

109
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,860
but she didn't go to the West Hall.

110
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,450
She went to the private garden.

111
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,720
Report!

112
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,280
Reporting to Madam.

113
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,480
An intruder broke into Qiwu Courtyard's private garden.

114
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,440
The Commander has surrounded them.

115
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,280
I'm here to ask for your permission.

116
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:32,000
May we enter the garden to catch them?

117
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:35,200
How dare they break into the Governor's Mansion on my birthday.

118
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:38,120
I'd like to see who has such audacity.

119
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:43,240
The intruder's background is unknown.

120
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:45,120
Please allow me to stay by your side

121
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,450
to protect you, Mother.

122
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,600
Fire!

123
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:52,840
The private garden is on fire! Put it out!

124
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,000
Fire!

125
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,890
Hurry, put out the fire!

126
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:00,440
What happened?

127
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:03,160
How could such a big fire start out of nowhere?

128
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,040
Reporting to Madam.

129
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,440
I had my men surround the garden.

130
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:09,000
The thief must be desperate.

131
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,320
They set this fire to escape.

132
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:12,380
I've ordered all exits to be blocked.

133
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:13,960
The Qiong flower!

134
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:17,800
You must not let anything happen to the Qiong flower.

135
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,760
Otherwise,

136
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:21,200
I'll have the entire Huben Guard buried with it.

137
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,120
Yes, Madam.

138
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,520
I will definitely protect the Qiong flower.

139
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,520
Mother! Mother!

140
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:26,840
The Qiong flower.

141
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,320
My Qiong flower!

142
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,800
Don't worry, Mother.

143
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,330
I'll go save the flower too.

144
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:58,600
Young Master.

145
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,680
They're not here.

146
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:10,180
Head towards Shangmu Courtyard.

147
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,300
Fainted from the heavy smoke.

148
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,360
The thief must still be in the garden.

149
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,000
Search carefully.

150
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,860
Young Master, what should we do? Should we save her?

151
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,960
Since she's not the Young Madam,

152
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,600
cancel the flower bestowal.

153
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,720
Take the Qiong flower away.

154
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:44,280
Marrying into the mansion as a substitute...

155
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,040
Could it be for this Qiong flower?

156
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:47,300
I'll go distract them.

157
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,320
Who's there? Stop!

158
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:52,640
Chase him!

159
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:57,720
Hold on!

160
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,580
Don't die in this trap.

161
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:26,160
Please go back, Third Young Master.

162
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:27,280
Madam has taken her medicine

163
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,280
and is resting now.

164
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,320
Regarding the private garden,

165
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:31,520
Madam is still deeply troubled,

166
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,560
especially about the Viburnum macrocephalum flowers in the garden.

167
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,280
They were all given by the Commander-in-Chief,

168
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:37,160
and Madam loved them very much.

169
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:38,560
It's all my fault.

170
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:41,360
Please ask Mother to take good care of herself.

171
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:44,360
This is the bracelet Madam gave you.

172
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:54,760
Father, I know I was wrong.

173
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:55,920
That floral amber bracelet

174
00:10:55,920 --> 00:10:58,360
is the only keepsake my mother left me.

175
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:01,400
I beg you, Father, don't destroy it.

176
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,160
Madam suddenly fell ill,

177
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,680
and the cause is unknown.

178
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:05,560
The diviner said

179
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:07,360
only by destroying what the Young Master cherishes most

180
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,760
can the illness be cured.

181
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:11,040
Young Master, this is filial piety.

182
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:13,400
The Commander-in-Chief ordered you to copy the Classic of Filial Piety.

183
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:15,560
Don't you understand?

184
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:18,360
Mother...

185
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,320
Shengyi.

186
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:35,160
My mother's bracelet!

187
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,620
My mother's bracelet.

188
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,560
Look what this is.

189
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:44,480
Why do you have it?

190
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:47,240
I searched all over the West Market these past two days

191
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,640
and found a similar one.

192
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,000
I secretly swapped them.

193
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,130
Those servants don't know any better.

194
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:54,920
They only destroyed a fake.

195
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,640
Smart, isn't it?

196
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,240
If she finds out,

197
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:00,370
she definitely won't let it go easily.

198
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,160
You're hurt.

199
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:04,960
Don't worry.

200
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:07,840
My father is the Commander of the Naval Forces,

201
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:10,040
and I am the daughter of a great general.

202
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:13,000
This little scratch is nothing.

203
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,200
Xin'er.

204
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,900
I don't have a mother anymore,

205
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:23,240
and now I don't even have a father.

206
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,640
Your father is out fighting wars.

207
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:28,000
Even though you're a hostage in the Commander-in-Chief's mansion,

208
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,360
you always protect me.

209
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,640
From now on,

210
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:34,000
you are my, Chu Shengyi's, only family.

211
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,520
If Madam Li ever makes things difficult for you in the future,

212
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:39,240
I will protect you even if it costs me my life.

213
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,360
Okay.

214
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:43,080
We are family for life.

215
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:46,000
A traveling merchant from the Western Regions

216
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:48,720
is bringing Viburnum macrocephalum seeds to the black market.

217
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:51,120
This merchant has just arrived in Kuizhou.

218
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:53,400
It's an extremely rare opportunity.

219
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:54,460
Madam ordered that

220
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,880
since the black market is not bound by Kuizhou's laws

221
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,400
and officials cannot easily intervene,

222
00:12:58,400 --> 00:13:01,680
the Third Young Master must go and get them personally this time.

223
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:04,880
If the Third Young Master fails to bring back those seeds,

224
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:08,720
it won't just be this bracelet that shatters.

225
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,040
I

226
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:14,640
will obey.

